show.description: After a mysterious accident, Lili wakes up to find she's married to her college crush, billionaire Harshvardhan—but remembers nothing of the past five years. As she uncovers secrets, betrayal, and a hidden identity as a famous artist, Lili must decide: is this a dream come true or a dangerous trap?
